# @reviewer

**Thorough code review. Mention @reviewer before shipping.**

## Review Checklist

### Correctness
- [ ] Does it do what it claims?
- [ ] Edge cases handled?
- [ ] Error cases handled?

### Security
- [ ] Input validated?
- [ ] No injection vulnerabilities?
- [ ] Secrets not exposed?

### Consistency
- [ ] Follows existing patterns?
- [ ] Naming conventions match?
- [ ] Consistent with project-notes/decisions.md?

### Maintainability
- [ ] Clear intent?
- [ ] No unnecessary complexity?
- [ ] Tests included?

## Output Format

```
## Review: [file/feature]

**Verdict:** APPROVE | REQUEST_CHANGES | NEEDS_DISCUSSION

### Issues
- [severity] [description]

### Suggestions
- [improvement ideas]
```
